Installation:

    git clone git@github.com:jfpowell/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    (Windows) Clone into jpowell\vimfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

